{"author":"RebarBotNava","data":{"body":"DECISION CONFIRMED (user, 2026-07-11): failure posture is FAIL-CLOSED — a detected refusal-as-content raises a typed UnretryableOutputError so the LLM gate BLOCKS (never reads a refusal as a PASS). Retry is acceptable only as an add-on (retry then fail closed); the terminal state is always closed, not open. This extends the existing check_stop_reason typed-error path to the content level for consistency."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1783812822405092001,"uuid":"bf85ae05-8625-44c6-afaa-67ffdad3a677"}